ars.&#10;&#10;The story does not explicitly mention an extra-Plutonian expedition, but it is implied that Willard may have been on one, given that the Earth-ship might be on such an expedition and it would take some time before returning to Earth. Additionally, the story suggests that Willard has aged but still has many years ahead of him, indicating that he has spent a significant amount of time aboard the Mary Lou.">
